      <!-- ====== RESPONSE SCHEMA ====== -->
      <h2 id="schema" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:40px">响应结构 /api/v1/today.json</h2>
      <div class="card card-glass" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:20px">
        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px">
          <thead><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
            <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 16px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;color:var(--color-text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;width:110px">字段</th>
            <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 16px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;color:var(--color-text-muted);text-transform:uppercase;width:80px">类型</th>
            <th style="text-align:left;padding:10px 16px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;color:var(--color-text-muted);text-transform:uppercase">说明</th>
          </tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">date</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">ISO 日期 YYYY-MM-DD（UTC 时区）</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">generatedAt</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">ISO 8601 生成时间戳</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">preset</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">预设标识符 (kebab-case)</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">presetName</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">人类可读名称</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">cssVars</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">object</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">34 个 CSS 自定义属性键值对（5 组：Colors / Typography / Spacing / Effects / Ambient）。颜色变量自动附带 <code>-rgb</code> 通道变体</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">customCss</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">主题专属 CSS（动画 keyframes、特效样式）。无自定义 CSS 时为空字符串 <code>""</code></td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">extensions</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">array</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">声明式装饰元素数组，支持 <code>floating</code> 和 <code>decorative</code> 两种类型。无扩展时为空数组 <code>[]</code>。最多 20 个。</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">logoText</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">主题 Logo 文字标识</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">logoColors</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">array</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">Logo 渐变色 hex 字符串数组。无 Logo 颜色时为空数组 <code>[]</code></td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">available</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">number</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">可用主题总数</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">directory</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">array</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">轻量索引 <code>[{'\{'}preset, name, primary, accent, logoText{'}\}'}]</code></td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">dailyIsCommunity</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">boolean</td><td style="padding:9px 16px"><code>true</code> 表示今日主题来自社区投稿</td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:600">apiVersion</td><td style="padding:9px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-muted)">string</td><td style="padding:9px 16px">API 版本号，当前为 <code>"v1"</code></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-muted" style="font-size:12px;margin-bottom:14px"><code>/api/v1/theme/{'{preset}'}.json</code> 结构一致，但不含 <code>date</code>、<code>generatedAt</code>、<code>available</code>、<code>directory</code>。</p>

