            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)"><td style="padding:8px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:600">customCss</td><td style="padding:8px 16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px">≤ 16 KB</td><td style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px">截断；<code>@import</code>、<code>url(http)</code>、<code>expression()</code>、<code>javascript:</code> 剥离</td></tr>
