  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{'{'}"name":"My Theme","author":"You","cssVars":{'{'}"--color-primary":"#ff6b6b","--color-bg":"#1a1a2e"{'}'},"customCss":"body {'{'} ... {'}'}","extensions":[{'{'}"type":"floating","char":"✨"{'}'}],"tags":["dark","vibrant"]{'}'}'</code></pre></div>
        <p class="text-muted" style="font-size:12px;margin-top:6px">必填: <code>name</code>, <code>author</code>, <code>cssVars</code>（必须含 <code>--color-primary</code> 和 <code>--color-bg</code>）。可选: <code>customCss</code>, <code>extensions</code>, <code>tags</code>（最多 5 个）。提交后进入审核队列。</p>
        <p class="text-muted" style="font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">成功响应 <code style="color:#22c55e">201</code>：<code>{'{'} success: true, theme: {'{'} id, name, ... {'}'}, warnings?: [...] {'}'}</code>。如果有 <code>warnings</code> 数组，说明部分字段被自动调整（如不支持的类型被移除）。</p>

        <h3 id="community-like" style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin:20px 0 12px">点赞</h3>
        <div class="cmd-group" style="margin-bottom:0"><div class="cmd-header"><span class="cmd-label">curl</span></div><pre class="cmd-block"><code>curl -X POST {siteUrl}/api/v1/diy/like.json \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{'{'}"id":"abc12345"{'}'}'</code></pre></div>
        <p class="text-muted" style="font-size:12px;margin-top:6px">服务器基于 IP + User-Agent 指纹去重，同一用户对同一主题仅计一次。返回 <code>{'{'}likes: number, voted: boolean{'}'}</code>。</p>
      </div>

