      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:36px">
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px 24px"><strong style="font-size:13px">1. 请求 API</strong> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:13px">— 页面加载时 GET <code>/api/v1/today.json</code>，尽早执行减少 FOUC</span></div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px 24px"><strong style="font-size:13px">2. 注入 CSS 变量</strong> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:13px">— 遍历 <code>cssVars</code>，逐条 <code>setProperty(k, v)</code> 到 <code>:root</code></span></div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px 24px"><strong style="font-size:13px">3. 注入特效</strong> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:13px">— <code>customCss</code> 非 null → 创建 <code>&lt;style&gt;</code>；<code>extensions</code> 非 null → 安全解析声明式元素（<code>createElement</code> + <code>textContent</code>）</span></div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px 24px"><strong style="font-size:13px">4. localStorage 缓存</strong> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:13px">— 存 date + cssVars + customCss，同日跳过网络请求</span></div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px 24px"><strong style="font-size:13px">5. 错误降级</strong> <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:13px">— fetch 失败 → 从 localStorage 恢复昨日主题 → CSS <code>var(--xxx, fallback)</code> 兜底</span></div>
